all over your face.

01:06:01.392 --> 01:06:03.089
- I don't have mango
all over my face.

01:06:03.133 --> 01:06:05.483
- It's all over your face.

01:06:05.526 --> 01:06:07.093
- Is it?
- Yeah!

01:06:09.617 --> 01:06:11.228
- Did I get it?
- No.

01:06:13.012 --> 01:06:14.796
- Well, I can't see it.
[Asha laughing]

01:06:14.840 --> 01:06:15.623
Is it?

