01:12:47.537 --> 01:12:48.407
He's very polite.

01:12:49.974 --> 01:12:51.279
We'll be married in July.

01:12:56.415 --> 01:12:57.460
- Do you love him?

01:12:59.244 --> 01:12:59.984
- Not yet.

01:13:02.552 --> 01:13:04.162
- I can't believe this.

