01:14:53.489 --> 01:14:56.622
- Shake my hand like a
businessperson and go inside.

01:14:56.666 --> 01:14:58.581
- Uh, it was a pleasure
talking with you,

01:14:58.624 --> 01:14:59.625
Miss?
