♪ Cannot stay ♪

01:37:43.118 --> 01:37:47.339
♪ All the precious moments ♪

01:37:47.383 --> 01:37:51.866
♪ Cannot stay ♪

01:37:51.909 --> 01:37:56.044
♪ It's not like
wings have fallen ♪

01:37:56.087 --> 01:38:00.831
♪ Cannot stay ♪

01:38:00.875 --> 01:38:05.053
♪ Without you
something's missin' ♪

01:38:05.096 --> 01:38:07.359
♪ Cannot say ♪

